* Pentachoron *

- Four dimensional rotation visualizer -

This application visualize the rotation of the simplest four dimensional object, the pentachoron[1]. It could rotate the object around the six basic planes with simple-, double- and isoclinic-rotation types. This application was inspired by the book Epoch[2].

[1] https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/5-cell
[2] http://www.specularium.org/peter-j-carroll/the-epoch

Sources: https://github.com/albertusoft/pentachoron
